<subSubSection id="68DEC5F83D76FF91FF1DFDEAFE7CFD13" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" type="description">
<paragraph id="207B96733D76FF91FF1DFDEAFE7CFD13" blockId="5.[151,1436,547,645]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
We have proposed and diagnosed three species groups inside the genus 
<taxonomicName id="E7C4EDF03D76FF91FC3AFDEAFBEDFDAA" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1903" box="[944,1030,547,572]" class="Arachnida" family="Anyphaenidae" genus="Patrera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="12B04A613D76FF91FC3AFDEAFBEDFDAA" box="[944,1030,547,572]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Patrera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: 
<taxonomicName id="E7C4EDF03D76FF91FB9EFDEAFB93FDAB" authorityName="Simon. Additionally" authorityYear="1903" box="[1044,1144,547,573]" class="Arachnida" family="Anyphaenidae" genus="Patrera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fulvastra">
<emphasis id="12B04A613D76FF91FB9EFDEAFB93FDAB" box="[1044,1144,547,573]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">fulvastra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E7C4EDF03D76FF91FB0EFDEAFB26FDAB" authorityName="Duperre &amp; Tapia" authorityYear="2016" box="[1156,1229,547,573]" class="Arachnida" family="Anyphaenidae" genus="Patrera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="philipi">
<emphasis id="12B04A613D76FF91FB0EFDEAFB26FDAB" box="[1156,1229,547,573]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">philipi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="E7C4EDF03D76FF91FA83FDEAFABBFDAB" authorityName="Martínez &amp; Brescovit &amp; Villarreal &amp; Oliveira" authorityYear="2021" box="[1289,1360,547,573]" class="Arachnida" family="Anyphaenidae" genus="Patrera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="florezi">
<emphasis id="12B04A613D76FF91FA83FDEAFABBFDAB" box="[1289,1360,547,573]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">florezi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, based on sexual characters. When specimens were unavailable, we assigned species to the groups based on originally published illustrations.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
